<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42014a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42014a">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42014a"> 14(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> confessor advances / then retreats / to ambush</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">After the first steps of advance, he <font color="green">[the confessor]</font> is advised to make several steps back, and to put himself in a kind of spiritual ambuscade, to see the effect of his first advance. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 45</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
